This project is a responsive YouTube Homepage clone built using HTML and CSS. It recreates the main layout and visual style of YouTube, including the navigation header, search bar, sidebar menu, category buttons, and a responsive video grid.

The page is designed to adapt to different screen sizes, providing a smooth experience on desktop computers, tablets, and mobile devices. CSS Flexbox, Grid, and media queries are used to organize the layout and make the interface responsive.

This project was created to practice front-end development skills, improve understanding of responsive web design, and gain experience building modern website layouts using only HTML and CSS.

Main features include:

* Responsive video grid layout
* YouTube-style navigation bar
* Sidebar navigation menu
* Search bar and header icons
* Video thumbnails and information sections
* Responsive design for desktop, tablet, and mobile screens
* Clean and organized HTML and CSS structure

Technologies used:

* HTML5
* CSS3
* CSS Flexbox
* CSS Grid
* Media Queries
